(Sets laser start position from operator-jogged center point)
(Stores only X/Y. Z is managed in a separate Z-touch flow.)

o<laser_set_start_xy> sub
    #5181 = #1
    #5182 = #2
    #5183 = #3
    (DEBUG, LASER: start XY saved to #5181/#5182, probe RPM #5183)
o<laser_set_start_xy> endsub

M2
